backoName().notice: Returns the name of this backo

creatorCanWithdrawFund().notice: Returns true if creator can withdraw funds, false otherwise

creatorWithdrawFund().notice: Collect funds from your members and end the round

getNextWithdrawBlock().notice: Returns the block number of which the creator can end the round and collect funds

getNumberOfLevels().notice: Returns the number of membership levels for this backo

getNumberOfMembers().notice: Returns the number of members subscribed to this backo

getWeiPerRound().notice: Returns the wei per round to this backo for the current round

initialize(string,string,string,address,.notice: Initialize the state of this backo contract

ipfsDataHashes().notice: Returns the hash addresses of the profile image and backo details stored on IPFS

isMember(address).notice: Returns true if `_address` is a member, false otherwise

lastWithdrawBlock().notice: Returns the block of which the creator withdrew fund last

levelInfos(uint256).notice: Returns the level information of the given id

memberInfos(address).notice: Returns the member information of the given address

minBlocksPerRound().notice: Returns the minimum amount of blocks per withdraw by the creator

removeFund().notice: Remove funds and unsubscribe from this backo

roundsDone().notice: Returns the number of rounds done by the backo. One round is done when the creator withdraws funds

setBackoDetailsHash(string).notice: Set the profile backo details address to be `_backoDetailsHash`

setCreatorAddress(address).notice: Set the creator address to be `_newCreator`

setProfileImageHash(string).notice: Set the profile image hash address to be `_profileImageHash`
